I agree with your list completely. I think the order listed is indicitive of what most of us feel as to whats most important. I too have several charcopys of the sorcerer and the matter line does need aecc. But the spec is fun to play on my matter sorcerer. Our survivability if we have any has got to be improved especially in light of all the magic resists in the game. I understand resists are a global issue but with our DD spells so watered down we feel it alot more.  The only reason matter spec works is due to people not building that resist line up as high as body or energy. 
