				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Bottom line lets face it more hp or a pet that absorbs damage will not do it.  We are Albs main CC.  What we need is an insta stun.  
<br />

<br />
The game has become an insta.  Any class with an insta will use it first whether to interrupt, CC, or damage.
<br />

<br />
An insta AE stun would give us the time to run and fight another day.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
